      <title>为了应对美联储的转向，华尔街转向短期债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/to-trade-the-federal-reserve-s-pivot-wall-street-turns-to-short-dated-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[发挥美联储转向货币宽松政策的最佳方式是买入期限较短、收益率仍超过 4% 的债务。]]></description>
